        <h2>Initial Release - Version 1.0.0</h2>
        <p>The first public release of SoundMindAI!</p>
        <h3>Features</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Recording:</strong> Capture system audio and microphone simultaneously</li>
          <li><strong>AI Transcription:</strong> OpenAI Whisper, AssemblyAI, or free Apple Speech</li>
          <li><strong>AI Summarization:</strong> Claude, GPT-4, Gemini, HuggingFace, OpenRouter</li>
          <li><strong>Organization:</strong> Tags, folders, and powerful search</li>
          <li><strong>Export:</strong> Multiple formats including TXT, Markdown, HTML, SRT</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> All data stored locally with BYOK model</li>
        </ul>
